(182, '_transient_ti_about_plugin_info_elementor', 'O:8:\"stdClass\":22:{s:4:\"name\";s:22:\"Elementor Page Builder\";s:4:\"slug\";s:9:\"elementor\";s:7:\"version\";s:5:\"2.9.8\";s:6:\"author\";s:115:\"<a href=\"https://elementor.com/?utm_source=wp-plugins&utm_campaign=author-uri&utm_medium=wp-dash\">Elementor.com</a>\";s:14:\"author_profile\";s:37:\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/pojome\";s:12:\"contributors\";a:7:{s:8:\"elemntor\";a:3:{s:7:\"profile\";s:39:\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/elemntor\";s:6:\"avatar\";s:88:\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/95d2d03d56fea4b55fcde4d62722953a?s=96&d=monsterid&r=g\";s:12:\"display_name\";s:9:\"Elementor\";}s:7:\"kingyes\";a:3:{s:7:\"profile\";s:38:\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/kingyes\";s:6:\"avatar\";s:88:\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/77687afd3880fb9ad19abc54f4c706df?s=96&d=monsterid&r=g\";s:12:\"display_name\";s:12:\"Yakir Sitbon\";}s:8:\"arielk-1\";a:3:{s:7:\"profile\";s:39:\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/arielk-1\";s:6:\"avatar\";s:88:\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8d9644549f9462ff7529f05d22a3686f?s=96&d=monsterid&r=g\";s:12:\"display_name\";s:6:\"ArielK\";}s:10:\"jzaltzberg\";a:3:{s:7:\"profile\";s:41:\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/jzaltzberg\";s:6:\"avatar\";s:88:\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/31c80d5f3dbb0df7ffaa89f43678d1ec?s=96&d=monsterid&r=g\";s:12:\"display_name\";s:14:\"Kobi Zaltzberg\";}s:8:\"mati1000\";a:3:{s:7:\"profile\";s:39:\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/mati1000\";s:6:\"avatar\";s:88:\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/652ff3b9594033ddb9b827f51aae26f6?s=96&d=monsterid&r=g\";s:12:\"display_name\";s:13:\"Mati Horovitz\";}s:6:\"pojosh\";a:3:{s:7:\"profile\";s:37:\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/pojosh\";s:6:\"avatar\";s:88:\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/75b01acab5921ca64af0d307c1f2065a?s=96&d=monsterid&r=g\";s:12:\"display_name\";s:6:\"pojosh\";}s:10:\"bainternet\";a:3:{s:7:\"profile\";s:41:\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/bainternet\";s:6:\"avatar\";s:88:\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1cdd42c841a307d7460954942e71877e?s=96&d=monsterid&r=g\";s:12:\"display_name\";s:10:\"Bainternet\";}}s:12:\"requires_php\";s:3:\"5.6\";s:7:\"ratings\";a:5:{i:5;i:4838;i:4;i:148;i:3;i:51;i:2;i:33;i:1;i:114;}s:11:\"num_ratings\";i:5184;s:15:\"support_threads\";i:266;s:24:\"support_threads_resolved\";i:28;s:15:\"active_installs\";i:4000000;s:8:\"homepage\";s:87:\"https://elementor.com/?utm_source=wp-plugins&utm_campaign=plugin-uri&utm_medium=wp-dash\";s:8:\"sections\";a:6:{s:11:\"description\";s:16158:\"<p><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe class=\'youtube-player\' type=\'text/html\' width=\'640\' height=\'360\' src=\'https://www.youtube.com/embed/kB4U67tiQLA?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;fs=1&#038;autohide=2&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;wmode=transparent\' allowfullscreen=\'true\' style=\'border:0;\'></iframe></span></p>\n<p>Il est temps d‚Äôutiliser un constructeur de page en direct, sans aucune limite de conception. Un constructeur de pages qui offre des conceptions de page haut de gamme et des fonctionnalit√©s avanc√©es, jamais vues sur WordPress.</p>\n<p>It&rsquo;s time for <strong><a href=\"https://elementor.com/?utm_source=wp-repo&amp;utm_medium=link&amp;utm_campaign=readme\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Elementor Page Builder</a></strong>.</p>\n<h4>Plus rapide. Bien plus rapide.</h4>\n<p>Instant reaction was a key feature we wanted to achieve. And we did. Instant drag &amp; drop page builder, instant live edit, instant page load. The speed of Elementor is not matched by any other page builder, free or paid. This makes the interface fun and easy to work with, as well as reduces the time it takes to design.</p>\n<h4>Conception en direct. R√©ellement en direct.</h4>\n<p>Never again work on the backend and guess what the frontend will look like. With Elementor page builder, you edit the page and simultaneously see exactly how it looks like. Elementor features live design &amp; inline editing, so the whole process of writing and designing is done directly on the page, with no need to press update or go to preview mode. It also works perfectly with or without Gutenberg.</p>\n<h4>Des surprises que vous ne verrez nulle part ailleurs.</h4>\n<p>With Elementor&rsquo;s unique features, you can create websites that have that certain &lsquo;designer touch&rsquo;. Among our page builder features are: Box Shadows, Background Overlays, Hover Effects, Headline Effects, Animations, Shape Dividers, Gradient Backgrounds and much more.</p>\n<h4>Pre-Designed Templates &amp; Blocks</h4>\n<p>Choose from 100+ of beautiful full page <a href=\"https://library.elementor.com/?utm_source=wp-repo&amp;utm_medium=link&amp;utm_campaign=readme\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">WordPress templates</a> and customize them to make them your own. You can also build your page by choosing from 300+ Blocks.</p>\n<p>Blocks are pre-designed section templates that can be easily combined into any page. Blocks include a variety of categories: services, testimonials, call to action and more. Save and reuse Elementor templates on different pages, or export them to a different website with a click.</p>\n<h4>Mobile First. Mobile Editing.</h4>\n<p>Elementor Page Builder comes with an exclusive toolset, that lets you create truly a responsive website in a whole new and visual way. From different font size, padding and margin per device, to reverse column ordering, this is the most powerful mobile page builder for creating perfect responsive websites.</p>\n<h4>Undo / Redo &amp; Revision History.</h4>\n<p>Our page builder includes undo and redo for any action you make. Click on Ctrl / Cmd + Z, or browse through the complete list of actions. Want to go back ever further? Switch to Revisions to view a complete list of all earlier saved versions of the page.</p>\n<h4>Canvas. Un mod√®le de page vierge pour les pages d&rsquo;atterrissage.</h4>\n<p>Design your entire page in the page builder. No header, no footer, just Elementor. This is perfect for landing pages and coming soon pages. Canvas works on any theme, and lets you get rid of the header area so you get a blank template to work on.</p>\n<h4>Modes maintenance &#038; en construction int√©gr√©s.</h4>\n<p>Need to get your site offline for maintenance? Use Elementor page builder&rsquo;s built in Maintenance Mode &amp; Coming Soon feature to show your visitors an under construction / coming soon page.</p>\n<h4>Esayez Elementor Pro. Le meilleur constructeur de page pour WordPress.</h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://elementor.com/pro/?utm_source=wp-repo&amp;utm_medium=link&amp;utm_campaign=readme\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Elementor Pro</a> am√©liore consid√©rablement votre flux de travail de conception et vous permet de concevoir plus rapidement et mieux que jamais. Avec Elementor Pro, tout se fait visuellement et sans code.</p>\n<p>Making changes to your theme shouldn&rsquo;t be so hard. Endless coding, dealing with developers, switching themes. The <a href=\"https://elementor.com/theme-builder/?utm_source=wp-repo&amp;utm_medium=link&amp;utm_campaign=readme\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Theme Builder</a> in Elementor Pro turns the entire process of creating WordPress websites 100% visual including your site&rsquo;s header, footer, single post and archive page design.</p>\n<p>Il existe de nombreuses autres <a href=\"https://elementor.com/features/?utm_source=wp-repo&amp;utm_medium=link&amp;utm_campaign=readme\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">fonctionnalit√©s</a> pour vous aider √† construire de meilleurs sites web¬†:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Visual and intuitive form builder</li>\n<li>Marketing automation and CRM integrations</li>\n<li>Polices personnalis√©es</li>\n<li>Role manager</li>\n<li>Blog post layout widget</li>\n<li>Image &amp; video sliders</li>\n<li>WooCommerce</li>\n<li>Widgets globaux</li>\n<li>CSS personnalis√©</li>\n<li>Animated headlines</li>\n<li>Et bien plus.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Join the elite web professionals who enjoy <a href=\"https://